.modal-window__close, .modal-window__close:hover, .modal-window__close:focus { background-image: url("https://mkt-static.bitly.com/static/1761593096/pages/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/close.svg"); background-size: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-color: transparent; position: absolute; right: 40px; top: 25px; }
